# Direct (top-level) dependencies for the calcubot server.
#
# This is the hand-edited source. After changing it, regenerate the fully-pinned
# lock in requirements.txt (run from the server/ directory):
#
#   docker run --rm -v "$PWD:/w" -w /w python:3.14-slim-trixie \
#     sh -c "pip install -q pip-tools && pip-compile --strip-extras requirements.in"
#
# requirements.txt is the generated lock — it pins every transitive dependency,
# is what the Docker image installs, and is the file Dependabot scans for
# vulnerabilities (so transitive deps like starlette are now watched too).

